data.description: Updated 2 Bedroom Single Story That Backs To Walking Trails And Green Belt. Home Has Upgraded Kitchen With Granite Counters, Gas Stove, There Are Wood Floors Throughout, Large Master Bedroom, Lots Of Natural Light, Large Patio And Open Space. Newer HVAC System. Updated Bathroom, Large Covered Patio With Dual French Doors. Enjoy Indoor Outdoor Living. The New Canopy Grove Green Space Directly Behind Features Walking Trails, Parks That Are Open To The Public And Offers Membership Availability For The New Pool/Gym. This is a Short sale.
